1) songs i have memmed...<br>
       tuyen's chant of frost and fire, fufil's DoT, charm, ensnare, hymn of restoration, lament, and run song of course<br>
2) sing run, and i suggest levi, (from singing steel boots)  pull a crowd by targetting a mob close to others...pull w/ either  chant of frost or fire...once they start coming towards make distance between you and them...keep the one you pulled targetted...hit him w/ charm...once it takes effect press F8 then your hotkey for /pet attack, then press /pet target...then back off and watch as they fight each other...in down time either sing run or health if you have been hit...after charm wears off repeat charm and targetting until your PET is almost dead...*make sure to watch pets health so he doesnt die and you lose the exp*<br>
3) once pet is almost dead, start running in a circle or a path hitting your pet w/ your DoTs until pet dies and you get the exp...then target a new victim and repeat....* MAKE SURE not to get your pet and other mobs confused...if you do then they will rather attack you then your pet and so it'll make this a little harder to complete...if that happens though, use ensnare on the one that is coming after you and get your pet to attack that specifc one...in this way the mob chasing you wont become a nuisance and will still die off =P....well i suppose that is it...just be careful out there and i hope this helps.... =D<br>
