<br>
Chant kiting. I get sow potions from my wife's shaman and twist chant of frost,fire,and curtailing.  Mobs drop really fast with those three dots on them(me running in circles around them.<br>
<br>
Charm kiting I like as well. basically the same as the post above.<br>
<br>
Fear kiting worked better than I thought it would.  The only problem being that the fear is an area effect, but if you choose the kite area carefully I havent had too much problem.  This also lets you keep those melee skills up.<br>
<br>
Well just thought I'd post what has been working for me now.  Oh and ding 47!!  Woot! <p><table cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2" border="0" width="100%">
